## Tested Environment

- Python 3.10
- TensorFlow 2.15, Keras 2.15 (Windows/Linux) / TensorFlow-macos 2.12, Keras 2.12 (Apple Silicon)
- Windows OS / macOS (Apple Silicon)

---

## Known Issues

- `model.export()` fails with a `ReplicaContext` error on some systems when saving
  after fine-tuning. Replaced with `tf.saved_model.save` using
  `experimental_custom_gradients=False`. This only affects the SavedModel format тАФ
  all other scripts use `baseline.keras`.

